cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a framework for resource allocation and power management in cloud computing systems using deep reinforcement learning. This involves dealing with high-dimensional state and action spaces, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The use of reinforcement learning also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the need to maintain system performance while minimizing power consumption suggests a focus on control systems (cs.SY).
